<BaseLayout title="Capital Gains Tax Guide 2026: Rates, Rules, and Strategies | ToolCalcs" description="Complete capital gains tax guide for 2026 including short-term vs long-term rates, NIIT, real estate exclusion, tax-loss harvesting, and crypto taxation rules." structuredData={structuredData}>
